name: Men's Capsuleer Elite XIX Hoodie
description:
The Capsuleers are considered an elite group across New Eden and this unique hoodie marks that status on Capsuleer Day XIX.

The YC124 celebrations of Capsuleer Day mark the 19th anniversary of the start of the Capsuleer Age, when cloned capsule-using spaceship pilots were given independent licenses in YC105. Capsuleer Day XIX is a time of celebration for "The Elite" among spaceship pilots, when New Eden looks back on the achievements of capsuleers and wonders what challenges, risks and opportunities the future may hold.
